<div id="review_2053862613" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2053862613" />
    <a title="Hannah Givens" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/16212834-hannah-givens"><img alt="Hannah Givens" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1602181662p2/16212834.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2053862613?book_show_action=true">Jul 08, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Hannah Givens" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Hannah Givens" href="/user/show/16212834-hannah-givens">Hannah Givens</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16212834-hannah-givens?shelf=childrens">childrens</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16212834-hannah-givens?shelf=animals">animals</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16212834-hannah-givens?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16212834-hannah-givens?shelf=short-stories">short-stories</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16212834-hannah-givens?shelf=poetry">poetry</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2053862613" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9118032515220239152">Memory is a funny thing... I remembered one line out of this whole book, and it&apos;s not even here. But it&apos;s still great. Not every story is anything special on its own, but there are a lot of wonderful authors combined here, and together all the stories make a collection that&apos;s slightly magical and a bit creepy and everything fairy tales should be. </span>
  <span id="freeText9118032515220239152" style="display:none">Memory is a funny thing... I remembered one line out of this whole book, and it's not even here. But it's still great. Not every story is anything special on its own, but there are a lot of wonderful authors combined here, and together all the stories make a collection that's slightly magical and a bit creepy and everything fairy tales should be. </span>
